title: Fix setup for operator documentation, make it navigable, update content using latest operator info.
body:
**Description**: 
Update to latest kernel and contrib op info
Fix double include of rank and html-proofer
Updates to Gemfile.lock from testing locally on Windows
Add the operator info to the navigation so they can be found

Setting 'markdown: GFM' in _config.yaml made the ContribOperators.md render correctly but disabled the kramdown toc functionality.

Kramdown breaks rendering ContribOperators.md if the dl tags aren't wrapped in a table (constantly increases the indent for every dl tag).

Hack around these issues.

Everything 'works' now but the layout is pretty crap for the operators pages (width doesn't adjust to page size, some text in columns overlaps the next column). Better than not being able to see the content at all though.

**Motivation and Context**
Fix documentation issues
